com.yworks.yfiles.graph

Interface IModelItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ILookup, ITagOwner
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IBend, IColumn, IEdge, ILabel, ILabelOwner, INode, IPort, IPortOwner, IRow, IStripe
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleBend, SimpleEdge, SimpleLabel, SimpleNode, SimplePort

    public interface IModelItem
extends ILookup, ITagOwner
    Base interface for items that can be used in a CanvasControl.

    Most prominently this is the interface all graph elements used in IGraph implement.

    It adds no functionality over the ILookup and ITagOwner interfaces it inherits.

    To add custom visuals to a CanvasControl it is not necessary to implement this interface. Instead, any object can be added directly to the canvas, provided there is a suitable ICanvasObjectDescriptor implementation for rendering it.
